===Noun===
'''[[fly]] [[on]] the [[wall]]'''
#{{idiom}} A [[quiet]], non-participating, or unseen [[observer]]; an [[eavesdropper]] or [[witness]].
#:''I'd like to be a '''fly on the wall''' when his father comes home and sees what the party did to his house.''

